							h2.comprehensive-intro__heading Fixed Income Investment
							h3.comprehensive-intro__subheading Fixed income are defensive investment product in nature
							div.row
								div.col-sm-6.fixed-investment__workflow
									div.fixed-investment__content
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-start Fixed Value Day
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-process
											div.fixed-investment__workflow-cell Your purchased debenture
												br
												| will be paid to At an agreed time interval
												br
												| the payout is guaranteed you at issue price at an agreed future date
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-end Guaranteed PrincipalRealized Income
								div.col-sm-6.fixed-investment__workflow
									div.fixed-investment__content
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-start Fixed Pay Day
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-process
											div.fixed-investment__workflow-cell At an agreed time interval the payout is guaranteed
												br
												| the payout is guaranteed
										+icon('l-arrow-down', 'blue')
										div.fixed-investment__workflow-end Realized Income
